00:00:18.859 --> 00:00:25.080
We're running out of time; it's very, very soon, Jesus is coming.

00:00:25.473 --> 00:00:29.009
So, I'm just going to be real open with you.

00:00:29.204 --> 00:00:35.399
Like I said, there are a lot of good people on here, and there are a lot of people that are struggling.

00:00:36.812 --> 00:00:42.059
God wants to do something with you, and He wants to bring breakthrough to your life.

00:00:44.172 --> 00:00:57.650
