00:01:15.960 --> 00:01:21.720
" He said, "They've cried out to me, 'God, where are you?

00:01:21.720 --> 00:01:24.189
I'm barely making it from paycheck to paycheck.

00:01:24.975 --> 00:01:27.960
I'm barely making it to feed my kids.

00:01:27.960 --> 00:01:34.780
' The single moms, the widow women, all the people who are really struggling.

00:01:34.780 --> 00:01:42.659
" There's a lot of people struggling, and He said, "I'm bringing forth a breakthrough for you.

00:01:42.659 --> 00:01:45.720
" There is a tidal wave of glory.

00:01:45.720 --> 00:01:49.337
There's a tidal wave of a financial turnaround.

00:01:49.337 --> 00:02:04.840
There are many of you that will go to bed one night, and if you listen to Him for direction on what He wants to do with your finances, you'll have a breakthrough overnight.

00:02:06.479 --> 00:02:13.379
